Quarter Ending: For the quarters ending June 2008 to March 2011 waiting times have been split into '0 - 6 weeks', '>6 - 9 weeks', '9 - 13 weeks', '>13 - 26 weeks' and '>26 weeks' timebands.
From the quarter ending June 2011 waiting times have been split into '0 - 6 weeks', '>6 - 9 weeks', '9 - 12 weeks', '>12 - 15 weeks', '>15 - 18 weeks' and '>18 weeks' timebands.

From the quarter ending June 2015, patients waiting over 18 weeks have been split into the timebands '>18 - 26 weeks', '>26 - 39 weeks', '>39 - 52 weeks', '>52 - 65 weeks', '>65 - 78 weeks', '>78 - 91 weeks', '>91 - 104 weeks', '>104 weeks', '>18 - 52 weeks' and '>52 weeks'.
